
= TLDRLegal: Lookup open source licenses summarized & explained in plain English.

URL = http://www.tldrlegal.com/


=Description=

"TL;DR provides information, tools and Professional Services related to Open Source Software (OSS) that can help vendors and users understand and use OSS more efficiently, and in a manner that helps reduce the risks of non-compliance.

When used smartly, OSS can help software developers be more competitive by reducing time to market, lowering development costs, and adding important functionality that might not otherwise be available.
TL;DR offers a full range of Professional Open Source Consulting Services, including OSS process reviews, program design and implementation, and training for development and legal teams. TL;DR can help you create custom written policies and low-touch processes designed to work with your existing development processes, and in a manner that helps protect your valuable Intellectual Property Rights."
